<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Double Slider Login/ Registration Form</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.lineicons.com/4.0/lineicons.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">

</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" id="container">
        <div class="form-container register-container" id="Formulario-Registro">
            <form action="/auth/register" method="POST">
                
                <h1><br>Registro</h1>
                <input type="text" name="newuser" id="newuser" placeholder="Username">
                <input type="text" name="Nombre" id="name" placeholder="Nombre Completo">
                <input type="text" name="apellidoP" id="apellidoP" placeholder="Apellido Paterno">
                <input type="text" name="apellidoM" id="apellidoM" placeholder="Apellido Materno">
                <input type="email" name="newemail" id="newemail" placeholder="Correo Electronico ">
                <input type="password" name="password1" id="password1" placeholder="Contraseña">
                <input type="password" name="password2" id="password2" placeholder="Confirmar Contraseña">
                <input type="tel" name="celular" id="celular" placeholder="Numero de celular">
                
                <div class="dropdown">
                    <label for="options"></label>
                    <select id="options" class="dropdown-select">
                        <option value="1">Trabajo Social</option>
                        <option value="2">Médico</option>
                        <option value="3">Administrativas</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <button type="submit">Guardar</button>
                <ul class="error" id="error1"></ul>



            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="form-container login-container" id="Login-Formulario">
            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <h1>Bienvenido</h1>
                <input type="text" name="username" id="username" placeholder="Nombre de Usuario">
                <div class="password-container">
                    <input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Contraseña">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <button class="btn" id="btn_ingresar">Ingresar</button>
                </div>
                <ul class="error" id="error"></ul>
                
            </form>
        </div>
        

    <div class="overlay-container">
        <div class="overlay">
            <div class="overlay-panel ovelay-left">
                <h1 class="title">¡Bienvenido <br>CRIT Hidalgo!</h1>
                <p>¿Ya tienes una cuenta autorizada?, Inicia sesión</p>
                <button class="ghost" id="login">Login
                    <i class="lni lni-arrow-left login"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="overlay-panel overlay-right">
                <h1 class="title">¡Registrate <br> CRIT Hidalgo! </h1>
                <p>Por favor, tenga en cuenta que la activación de su cuenta no será inmediata, un supervisor validara su solicitud.</p>
                <button class="ghost" id="register">Register
                    <i class="lni lni-arrow-right register"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    <script src="/public/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
